locations: New York City, New York, USA
imdb.plot outline: A unique series that offers insight into the underground world of the five boroughs of New York City. The show presents many pertinent subjects that a large demographic of the NYC population are routinely engaged in. Throughout the series the audience will see deep seeded mental conditions and the psychological trauma caused as a result of life changing challenges and circumstances. The characters struggle to find balance, also refrain from certain decisions that subsequently impact their lives and lives of people to who they are connected. "New York Underground Kingz" embodies truth, turmoil, triumph, defeat, beauty, love, and hate. The stories embrace crucial social dynamics and uncommon issues resulting in a very intimate and candid perspective on an array of topics. This powerful presentation incorporates elements of Kemetic Science and Hip Hop culture as a means of enlightenment and empowerment. The show capture the "only in New York" lifestyle and ambiance with authentic imagery of distinct neighborhoods that reflect the urban landscape. "New York Underground Kingz" is inspired by true events.
imdb.title: New York Underground Kingz
plot: Osiris and King David struggle to find duality as they navigate their way through the New York City underground. The enigmatic characters in their circles provide support and alliance as they attempt to rise to prominence in the New York underground.
